{
  "2318090": {
    "name": "Sole Salvation",
    "steam_appid": 2318090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/fb28b9b25f5b89a4b6e4b2355f04de68.avif?t=1771237412\" width=1280 height=360 /></span><br>探索一个<strong>古老组织</strong>的秘密，踏入 <strong>Valeriano</strong> 记忆中被腐蚀的土地——一个被卷入超越自身命运的少年。掌握<strong>宇宙神器</strong>，击败不断追捕你的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款<strong>动作类 Roguelite</strong>中，你可以同时使用远程武器和近战武器，通过组合连击、元素与技能，创造毁灭性的攻击链，消灭一切威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越各个区域，找回<strong>记忆</strong>，并在每一次尝试中变得更强……死亡后，你只会失去最微弱的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sole Salvation</strong> 是 <strong>METEORA</strong> 的首款游戏，这是一家由一名开发者独立组成的工作室。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌控你的武器，粉碎你的敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/e2194b47945ba2a362d2aa02ddc8d17f.poster.avif?t=1771237412\" width=790 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/e2194b47945ba2a362d2aa02ddc8d17f.webm?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/e2194b47945ba2a362d2aa02ddc8d17f.mp4?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在这款<strong>动作 Roguelite</strong>中，生存的关键在于掌握远程与近战武器的<strong>节奏</strong>和招式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏中你都会拥有两种<strong>武器类型</strong>：近战与远程。根据你的策略，随时自由切换并使用它们，无需手动装备或更换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/d8db2645bf872beaa5a95d61253441f3.poster.avif?t=1771237412\" width=790 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/d8db2645bf872beaa5a95d61253441f3.webm?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/d8db2645bf872beaa5a95d61253441f3.mp4?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种武器都有其<strong>独特的战斗风格</strong>、特点和<strong>连招</strong>，并会随着你在游戏中获得的大量技能与力量而进一步强化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合攻击，强化你的<strong>武器库</strong>，创造你自己的<strong>生存之道</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在每一次尝试中变得更强</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/ce98af66141791baabab9b547f0e3f11.poster.avif?t=1771237412\" width=790 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/ce98af66141791baabab9b547f0e3f11.webm?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/ce98af66141791baabab9b547f0e3f11.mp4?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一次尝试中收集 <strong>回声碎片</strong>，并用它们永久固定 <strong>Valeriano</strong> 的记忆。强化他的武器、技能和属性，让自己不断变强，粉碎阻挡你前进的生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与 <strong>虚影</strong> 接触——这些脆弱的记忆会在死亡时消散。收集数百种不同的虚影，每一种都受到你所选择武器的影响，打造属于你的独特构筑，让每一局都独一无二、不可重复。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡、调整你的策略，并提升你的 <strong>觉悟</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>被宇宙法则席卷的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/07b33da99d0fcebe26ef7da1ca8d50e9.poster.avif?t=1771237412\" width=790 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/07b33da99d0fcebe26ef7da1ca8d50e9.webm?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318090/extras/07b33da99d0fcebe26ef7da1ca8d50e9.mp4?t=1771237412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个<strong>隐藏的组织</strong>启动了“<strong>唯一救赎</strong>”事件。转瞬之间，人类被彻底吞没：人们的头颅从身体分离，静止地悬浮在半空中，凝视着撕裂天空的巨大光束。世界在<strong>宇宙力量</strong>的冲击下扭曲变形：破碎的景观、扭曲的建筑、被未知存在污染的现实碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演 <strong>Valeriano</strong>，事件的幸存者，被卷入一个远超自身的命运之中。迷失在梦幻般、不断变化的现实里，你必须在<strong>腐化的记忆</strong>与扭曲的幻象之间前行，揭开发动“唯一救赎”的组织的真意，拯救你所爱之人，并面对重新浮现的过去的<strong>救赎</strong>。</p>",
